{"tid":2313831,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［冇人講咪我講］今日岩田聰生日","createTime":"2020-12-06T06:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T11:48:48.000Z","uid":381591,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dcbe4ba0eec22bf4d165323a29ce4c3b820860ca","tid":2313831,"uid":381591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:20:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RMrj8gdUfCU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRMrj8gdUfCU&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=42084950\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RMrj8gdUfCU</a><br />\n<br />\n依段演講2005嘅，到今日再睇返依然一啲都唔out，仲好講到今時今日遊戲界嘅情況。論機能任天堂一定唔係最勁，但無可否認係佢有一套佢自己嘅哲學。<br />\n今日係岩田聰生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁大件事冇人講。"},{"pid":"41de8f8e3fabe96d38740d56cf8b80ad70bd5e54","tid":2313831,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"冇人講咪..."},{"pid":"30f1dd2ef3104525242c3f34e92f9337ea990609","tid":2313831,"uid":142179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"好多人話佢走咗之後任天堂仆街咗好多，點睇"},{"pid":"7e3d5ab2fb0664dcc0d9281a29d7e6934bbe83e0","tid":2313831,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/k4cJh2YgrKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fk4cJh2YgrKE&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=c70e7dc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/k4cJh2YgrKE</a><br />\n<br />\n佢真係好叻, 本身都係好勁的程式員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722bb5cbd5f3e055a00c3e849a9c6c591a69d05e","tid":2313831,"uid":381591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30f1dd2ef3104525242c3f34e92f9337ea990609","tid":2313831,"uid":142179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"好多人話佢走咗之後任天堂仆街咗好多，點睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T11:36:02.000Z","msg":"經營方針唔同左就一定，玩家最主要睇到都係一啲銷售策略/宣傳政策唔同左，但我覺得好難去判斷係唔係真係因為佢而唔同左，有啲野都係成敗論英雄，咁比較冇意思。"},{"pid":"f71509e8e7a893f0614b02ae7d80d817fc6ac369","tid":2313831,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T11:36:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YdDYoCU2kv0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYdDYoCU2kv0&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=7b4485db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YdDYoCU2kv0</a>"},{"pid":"770ade6673c73094722a36a65767e8a19ee8abfe","tid":2313831,"uid":381591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f71509e8e7a893f0614b02ae7d80d817fc6ac369","tid":2313831,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T11:36:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YdDYoCU2kv0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYdDYoCU2kv0&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=7b4485db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YdDYoCU2kv0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T11:48:48.000Z","msg":"以前啲direct好多花款，又會介紹下隻game嘅設計理念（但相對上會悶啲，資訊冇依家咁密集）<br />\n依家啲diect只係放新情報，少左花款同開發訪談。不過觀眾要求唔同左冇計，上次櫻井講左半個鐘大亂鬥比人鬧晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時都好想佢出返依類節目，唔一定要係direct入面，好似Botw咁單獨放上Youtube都好。"}]}